{"tid":820904,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[莫縮叔台] Marvel's Spider-Man (PS4)","createTime":"2018-09-15T16:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T16:14:25.000Z","uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31fea2c95f189bbba65db2103cf2fe5ddab15094","tid":820904,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"[莫縮叔台] Marvel's Spider-Man (PS4)<br />\n<br />\n莫縮叔遊戲台<br />\n每個星期五、六、日晚上，<br />\n跟大家一邊傾計，一邊打機<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fmokuncle%2F&d=dGBnwKlFC95%2Bi1g57x%2FFZ10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9c9f5257\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/</a><br />\n<br />\nMarvel's Spider-Man<br />\n<br />\n《Marvel's Spider-Man》的主角是全球知名的超級英雄蜘蛛人，這位攀牆者能夠施展招牌雜技能力、即興招式與高超的蛛絲發射技巧。除此之外，遊戲裡還有《Spider-Man》系列作中從未出現的元素。除了能以跑酷方式在城中穿梭游走，與環境進行特殊互動，還加入了全新的戰鬥和大場面動作，與你以往玩過的《Spider-Man》遊戲完全不同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://store.playstation.com/store/api/chihiro/00_09_000/container/HK/ch/999/HP9000-CUSA09893_00-ASIAPLACEHOLDER0/1536640870000/image?w=240&amp;h=240&amp;bg_color=000000&amp;opacity=100&amp;_version=00_09_000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.playstation.com%2Fstore%2Fapi%2Fchihiro%2F00_09_000%2Fcontainer%2FHK%2Fch%2F999%2FHP9000-CUSA09893_00-ASIAPLACEHOLDER0%2F1536640870000%2Fimage%3Fw%3D240%26h%3D240%26bg_color%3D000000%26opacity%3D100%26_version%3D00_09_000&h=bf50859b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n莫縮叔Facebook Page: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMokUncle&d=dGBnwKlFC95%2Bi1g57x%2FFZ10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=d1622ca4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle</a>"},{"pid":"d9c9e3a470139585effd83e40b68a49b116ad82e","tid":820904,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"<i